Revision history for LWP-UserAgent-ProgressAny

0.05    2015-01-22 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [Refactor] combine response_done & response_data handlers so less
	  code is duplicated.

	- [doc] Update/fix comparison with LWP::UserAgent::ProgressBar.

	- [doc] Mention HTTP::Tiny::ProgressAny.


0.04    2015-01-22 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [doc] Add screenshot.


0.03    2015-01-22 (PERLANCAR)

	- Show download size in message.


0.02    2015-01-22 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [Bugfix] Set memory variable per-request object (previously the
	  second and subsequent LWP requests do not get updated because the
	  memory variable was globally-scoped).


0.01     2015-01-20 (PERLANCAR)

         - First release.
